        <div class="flex-1 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-base">
            <p class="mb-4 text-slate-700">Once upon a time in the silicon valley of code, a nomadic <strong>Gopher</strong> (representing the speed of Go) met a versatile <strong>Duck</strong> (the mascot of adaptability). Together, they hatched a plan to create the most evolutionary code generator in the ecosystem.</p>
            <p class="text-slate-700">The result is <span class="font-bold text-indigo-600">GO-DUCK</span>. It doesn't just generate boilerplate; it evolves with your business logic. We integrated a chilled <strong>bottle of Gin</strong> for the most refreshing web routing and the divine <strong>mark of Kratos</strong> to ensure your microservices are armored with enterprise-grade gRPC resilience.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-6 p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100">
